      "text": "1. privatelink.cognitiveservices.azure.com        → AI Services PE\n2. privatelink.blob.core.windows.net                     → Storage Blob PEs (×2)\n3. privatelink.documents.azure.com                      → Cosmos DB PE\n4. privatelink.azurewebsites.net                            → Weather Function PE\n5. privatelink.queue.core.windows.net                   → Queue Storage PEs (×2)\n6. privatelink.file.core.windows.net                        → File Storage PE\n7. niceriver-877b9fd9.eastus2.azurecontainerapps.io → A: * and @ → 10.0.2.160",
